                data-aos="fade-right"
                data-aos-delay="100"
            >
                <h3 class="section-sub-heading" data-i18n="welcome_heading">
                    Welcome to Tharlam Academy
                </h3>
                <p class="section-tagline" data-i18n="welcome_tagline">
                    Where Wisdom Meets Modern Learning
                </p>
                <p data-i18n="welcome_paragraph_1">
                    Nestled in the heart of Kathmandu, Tharlam Academy is more
                    than just a school — it's a place where young minds grow
                    with knowledge, compassion, and purpose. Inspired by
                    Buddhist values and supported by a modern curriculum, we
                    offer students a well-rounded education rooted in tradition
                    and aimed at the future.
                </p>

                <h3 data-i18n="curriculum_overview_heading">
                    Curriculum Overview
                </h3>
                <p data-i18n="curriculum_overview_paragraph">
                    Tharlam Academy offers a unique curriculum spanning
                    pre-primary to secondary levels. Our integrated approach
                    empowers students by blending Buddhist traditions with
                    diverse modern subjects, preparing them for both academic
                    excellence and a values-based life.
                </p>

